##  Reflection:

While documenting today, I noticed that our team **does not yet have a formal checklist for log review signoffs**. This surfaced as a gap.  

**Next step as a leader:** I will propose adding a lightweight â€œWeekly Log Review Checklistâ€ in Confluence, signed off digitally â€” this builds auditability and clarity for this control.  

