##  Why This Work Is Critical:

> â€œPolicies and procedures are the connective tissue of a security program â€” without them, tech controls drift and decay.â€  

As I mentor newer GRC analysts, I remind them: **a well-written SSP is not fiction â€” it reflects reality.** If we find gaps while writing, we fix the process, then document it.

